DATA & METHODOLOGY ATTRIBUTION
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

This tool synthesizes publicly available data from the following sources.
Original data and methodology rights belong to respective publishers:

- DOE/NETL (Cost and Performance Baseline Reports, QGESS Methodology)
- IEAGHG (Technical Reports, Solvent R&D, Calcium Looping, Cement CCS)
- IRS / U.S. Treasury (Section 45Q Tax Credit, IRA 2022)
- IPCC (Special Report on CCS, AR6 WG3)
- KIER (KIERSOL Pilot Reports)
- TotalEnergies / IFP-EN (3D Project, DMX Solvent)
- Mitsubishi Heavy Industries (KS-1 / KS-21 Solvents)
- Shell Cansolv (DC-103 Solvent)
- Aker Carbon Capture (S26 Solvent)
- Global CCS Institute (Status Reports)
- KRX, ICE, RVO Netherlands, UK BEIS/DESNZ
- Other peer-reviewed publications (cited in app Tab ⑦ References)

When reusing this tool or its outputs, please cite:
  Song, B. K. (2026). "CO₂ 포집·CCUS 기술·경제성 벤치마크 (CCUS Tech-Economic
  Benchmark)". https://github.com/cafeon90-oss
